title: Privacy Impact Assessments Register
metadatasummary: This dataset is an abridged log of Privacy Impact Assessments (PIA) conducted by the Information Management and Security Team in 2017, recording privacy risks associated with new projects or policies involving personal data processing within organizations. The PIA is a process recommended by the Information Commissioner. Each entry in the log includes an enquiry log reference number and the type of personal data processing covered by the PIA.

title: Privacy Impact Assessments Register
metadatasummary: This dataset is an abridged version of the Information Management and Security Team's Privacy Impact Assessments log, recording and tracking assessments made on privacy risks associated with new projects or policies involving personal data processing. The enquiry log reference number is linked to a central log, while the 'type' attribute denotes the kind of personal data processing covered by each assessment.

title: Information Management and Security Team Enquiry Log
metadatasummary: The "Information Management and Security Team Enquiry Log" is an abridged version of logs recording, tracking, and reporting enquiries received by the Information Management and Security Team at the Food Standards Agency in 2017. These enquiries concern any aspect of information governance, security, records management, data protection, and use of the FSA corporate records management system.

title: Information Management and Security Team Enquiry Log
metadatasummary: The "Information Management and Security Team Enquiry Log" is an abridged version of logs documenting enquiries made to the Information Management and Security Team at the Food Standards Agency, recording, tracking, and reporting on all received inquiries. These inquiries pertain to any aspect of information governance, security, records management, data protection, and usage of the FSA corporate records management system.

title: Information Management and Security Team Enquiry Log
metadatasummary: The "Information Management and Security Team Enquiry Log" is an abridged version of queries logged by the Food Standards Agency's team, offering advice on information governance, security, records management, data protection, and FSA corporate records management system use.
